			<h2>Gleb Mikulich</h2>		
			<h5>Expertise in supply chain, procurement, logistics, and digital transformation</h5>		
		<p>Gleb Mikulich is a seasoned professional with over a decade of expertise in supply chain, procurement, logistics, and digital transformation. He has collaborated with globally recognized organizations, including Accenture, Procter &amp; Gamble (P&amp;G), Pfizer, CNH Industrial, and Mediterranean Shipping Company, delivering impactful solutions across diverse industries.</p>
<p>Gleb holds esteemed certifications in Procurement and Supply Chain Management. These qualifications underscore his dedication to excellence and continuous professional development.</p>
<p>A graduate of the prestigious <strong>IE Business School</strong>, Gleb earned his MBA with a focus on strategy, operations, and digital technologies, where he was inducted as a lifetime member of <strong>Beta Gamma Sigma</strong>. He further enhanced his expertise through advanced studies in supply chain management at<strong>MITx</strong>. His exceptional contributions to the industry have been recognized with numerous honors. Beyond his corporate achievements, Gleb has over five years of experience mentoring young professionals. He is driven by his passion for cultivating the next generation of leaders in supply chain and procurement. As an instructor, Gleb is eager to share his wealth of knowledge, foster dynamic discussions, and learn from his students' diverse experiences.</p>
<p>With a commitment to innovation and professional growth, Gleb Mikulich brings unparalleled expertise and inspiration to every engagement.</p>
